Partially overlap: 𝑝_1 VS. 𝑝_6 (change)(𝑝_6=𝑃𝑟𝑜𝑗(𝐺(𝑝_1 ),𝑓_2))If 𝑝_1 is true, 𝑝_6 is true (but we don’t care)If 𝑝_6 is true, 𝑝_1 is not guaranteed true.


